==Russian==
===Possessive pronoun===
'''своём''' (svojóm) {{m}} or {{n}} {{s}}

# [[one's]], [[my]], [[his]], [[her]], [[its]], [[our]], [[your]], [[their]] ''(always refers to the subject of the sentence) ([[prepositional case]] of [[свой]])''
#:[[она|Она]] [[говорить|говорит]] [[о#Russian|о]] '''своём''' [[сын|сыне]] — ''She’s talking about her son (her own son).''
#:Она говорит о '''[[её]]''' сыне — ''She’s talking about her son (another lady’s son).''